steps.codeSnippet:
In the Send Email node:

1. To Email: {{ $json.Email }}
2. Subject: New submission from {{ $json.Name }}
3. Text: 
   Hello {{ $json.Name }},

   Thank you for your submission!
   Message: {{ $json.Message }}

   Best regards,
   Your Automated Assistant

Note: Replace 'Email', 'Name', 'Message' with your actual column names
